Package: hydatr
Type: Package
Title: An R Interface to the Environment Canada HYDAT database
Version: 0.1.9000
Author: Dewey Dunnington <dewey@fishandwhistle.net>
Maintainer: Dewey Dunnington <dewey@fishandwhistle.net>
Description: The HYDAT database contains over 1 GB of hydrological
  observation data collected by Environment Canada. The database
  is freely available from the Environment Canada website, however
  exctracting data can be difficult. This package provides tools to
  easily find and extract hydrological data from the HYDAT database.
Imports: stringr, xml2, curl, dplyr, dbplyr, RSQLite, magrittr, utils, 
    lubridate, plyr, tibble, reshape2, prettymapr
Suggests: testthat, httr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
